T02TD2727E:95a-1: shr'i kharsa p'a na lo ka n'a tha s'a dha na n'a ma /
T02TD2727E:95a-3: dpal 'jig rten mgon po la spyod pa'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD2727E:95a-4: 'jig rten mgon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2727E:95a-5: dpal ldan mngon 'dod 'bras bu ster ba'i gzi ldan dpag bsam rkang 'thung ni //
T02TD2727E:95a-6: bde bar gshegs rnams bzhed pa'i don chen bzod mdzad ded dpon chen po ste //
T02TD2727E:95a-7: srid dang zhi ba mnyam pa'i dngos gyur dngos po kun gyi ngo bo nyid //
T02TD2727E:95a-8: phyag na padma de yis 'gro ba'i sdig pa zhi bar mdzad du gsol //
T02TD2727E:95a-9: skye bos dben pa'i gnas dag tu //
T02TD2727E:95a-10: sngar langs kha gdong dag byas nas //
T02TD2727E:95a-11: 'jam pa'i stan la yang dag gnas //
T02TD2727E:95a-12: snying gar zla rgyas 'od gsal ba'i //
T02TD2727E:95a-13: steng du rang gi sa bon bsam //
T02TD2727E:95a-14: snying ga'i zla 'od kyis sa bon //
T02TD2727E:95a-15: yongs bskul de yi sa bon gyis //
T02TD2727E:95a-16: kharsa p'a na mgon dpal ldan //
T02TD2727E:95a-17: bla ma sangs rgyas de sras mchog / mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs la //
T02TD2727E:95a-18: sa bon de dag las byung ba'i //
T02TD2727E:95a-19: sna tshogs mchod pa'i sprin gyis mchod //
T02TD2727E:95a-20: de nas mngon par phyag byas nas //
T02TD2727E:95a-21: sdig pa bshags pa la sogs bya //
T02TD2727E:95a-22: thog med 'khor bar gang zhig rnam 'khor che //
T02TD2727E:95a-23: bdag gis mi dge bgyis dang bgyid stsal ba'am //
T02TD2727E:95a-24: gzhan gyis bgyis la rjes su yi rang ba //
T02TD2727E:95a-25: thams cad bcom ldan rnams kyis spyan sngar bshags //
T02TD2727E:95a-26: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang rgyal sras 'phags rnams dang //
T02TD2727E:95a-27: gzhan dag gis kyang dge ba gang bgyis la //
T02TD2727E:95a-28: rjes su yi rang de dag ma lus pa //
T02TD2727E:95a-29: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu ni yongs su bsngo //
T02TD2727E:95a-30: snying rje dam pa las 'khrungs pa'i //
T02TD2727E:95a-31: sangs rgyas rnams la skyabs su mchi //
T02TD2727E:95a-32: chos kun ro gcig rang bzhin can //
T02TD2727E:95a-33: gos pa med pa'i chos dag dang //
T02TD2727E:95a-34: rab dga' la sogs sar bzhugs pa'i //
T02TD2727E:95a-35: byang sems rnams la'ang de bzhin no //
T02TD2727E:95a-36: sangs rgyas mya ngan 'da' bzhed gyur pa rnams //
T02TD2727E:95a-37: gzhan la phan phyir yun du bzhugs par gsol //
T02TD2727E:95b-0: sgrib pa thams @95b cad dpyis 'byin gyur pa yi //
T02TD2727E:95b-1: rgyur gyur byang chub sems ni bskyed bgyi zhing //
T02TD2727E:95b-2: bde gshegs rnam dag lam gyi dgongs pa dang //
T02TD2727E:95b-3: rtag par yang dag kun nas bsten par bgyi //
T02TD2727E:95b-4: de nas rgyu dang mi rgyu'i 'gro ba 'di dag kun //
T02TD2727E:95b-5: gcig dang du ma rnam bral stong pa nyid du rnam bsam bya //
T02TD2727E:95b-6: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma konya\ham /
T02TD2727E:95b-7: zhes bya bas stong pa nyid lhag par gnas par bya'o //
T02TD2727E:95b-8: chos 'di dag thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis yongs su dag pa'o zhes lhag par gnas pa de ltar bdag nyid la'ang kun du bltas nas /
T02TD2727E:95b-9: aom sva bh'a wa shuddha:sarba dharm'a:sva bh'a wa shuddhony\ham /
T02TD2727E:95b-11: de nas sgom pa pos sngon gyi smon lam gyis yang dag par bskul ba'i rnam par shes pa tsam gyi pam yig yongs su gyur pa las kha dog sna tshogs pa'i padmar /
T02TD2727E:95b-12: aa yig las skyes pa'i dri ma med pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-13: de'i steng du hr'i:yig 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis nam mkha'i khyon kun yang dag par gsal ba bsam par bya zhing /
T02TD2727E:95b-14: de yongs su gyur pa las padma'i snying por rang gi sa bon 'od zer gyi phreng bas brgyan pa lta bar bya'o //
T02TD2727E:95b-15: de nas 'di dag yongs su gyur pa las bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das su bsam par bya ste /
T02TD2727E:95b-16: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'od ltar dkar ba'i sku can /
T02TD2727E:95b-17: ral pa bcings pa la dbu rgyan dang /
T02TD2727E:95b-18: spyi gtsug tu 'od dpag med bkod pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-19: sna tshogs padma dang zla ba la skyil grung phyed pas bzhugs pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-20: sku la mchog gi rgyan dang ldan zhing /
T02TD2727E:95b-22: brgyad gnyis lon pa'i lang tsho can /
T02TD2727E:95b-23: phyag g-yas mchog sbyin dang g-yon pa sdong bu dang bcas pa'i padma 'dzin pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-24: de'i 'og tu mdog lhag par nag pa'i yi dags gdong pa gyen du phyogs shing kha gdangs pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-25: gre ba khab kyi mig can /
T02TD2727E:95b-27: shin tu rid pa rnams phyag nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun sim par 'bab pa mthong bas tshim par mdzad pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-28: snying rjes brlan pa'i dpal dang ldan zhing gru 'dzin gyi ri bo'i spo la bzhugs pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-29: lhag par zhi bas rnam par gzigs pa can /
T02TD2727E:95b-30: sgeg pa'i nyams dang ldan pa /
T02TD2727E:95b-31: sna tshogs pa'i mtshan rnams kyis brgyan pa'o //
T02TD2727E:95b-32: de'i mdun du sgrol ma dang /
T02TD2727E:95b-33: g-yas logs su gzhan nu nor bzangs so //
T02TD2727E:96a-1: ljang gu phyag g-yon pas sdong bu dang bcas pa'i autpa la 'dzin cing /
T02TD2727E:96a-2: g-yas pas kha 'byed pa'i tshul can /
T02TD2727E:96a-3: sna tshogs pa'i rgyan dang ldan pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-4: lang tsho gzhon zhing nu 'bur rgyas pa'o //
T02TD2727E:96a-5: gzhon nu nor bzangs gser gyi mdog can /
T02TD2727E:96a-8: mchan khung g-yon du glegs bam bcug pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-9: rgyan thams cad dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD2727E:96a-10: rgyab tu khro gnyer can dang /
T02TD2727E:96a-12: de la khro gnyer can ser mo /
T02TD2727E:96a-14: ral ba'i cha shas rdzogs pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-15: g-yon pas dbyu gu gsum pa dang /
T02TD2727E:96a-17: g-yas pas phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul dang /
T02TD2727E:96a-20: rta mgrin mdog dmar po thung zhing gsus pa 'phyang ba /
T02TD2727E:96a-21: skra dmar ser gyen du 'bar ba /
T02TD2727E:96a-22: sbrul gyi mchod phyir thogs dang ldan pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-23: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la smar dmar ser gyis sbras pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-24: spyan gsum dmar zhing zlum pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-25: khro gnyer dang smin ma 'khyug pa /
T02TD2727E:96a-26: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs 'phyang ba /
T02TD2727E:96a-27: g-yon pas dbyug pa'i mtshon cha dang /
T02TD2727E:96a-28: g-yas pas phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul can te /
T02TD2727E:96a-29: 'di dag thams cad rang gi gtso bo la ji ltar mdzes pa'i mig dag gis blta zhing 'dug pa rnam par bsam par bya'o //
T02TD2727E:96a-30: de nas rang gi snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du hr'i: yig bsams la /
T02TD2727E:96a-31: de las rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i 'od zer 'phros pas /
T02TD2727E:96a-32: khams gsum po yongs su gang zhing sems can thams cad 'jig rten dbang phyug gi go 'phang la rab tu bkod nas /
T02TD2727E:96a-34: sa bon gyi yi ge de la gzhug par bya'o //
T02TD2727E:96a-35: phyi nas 'od zer de nyid kyis ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs te /
T02TD2727E:96a-36: dam tshig sems dpa' dang chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa ltar gcig tu gyur pa'i skur bsam par bya'o //
T02TD2727E:96a-37: de nas lus ngag yid gsum rnam par dag par bya bya ste /
T02TD2727E:96a-38: rim pa ji lta bar spyi bor aom yig dkar po dang /
T02TD2727E:96a-39: mgrin par a'a: yig dmar po dang /
T02TD2727E:96a-40: thugs kar h'um yig sngon po rnams bsams la /
T02TD2727E:96a-41: 'di rnams las mtha' yas pa'i 'od zer gyi dra brtag tu 'phros pas /
T02TD2727E:96a-42: sems can gyi phung po thams cad kyi sdig pa'i tshogs gzhom par bya'o zhes nus pa ji lta bas gsal ba bsgom par bya'o//
T02TD2727E:96b-0: @96b rnal 'byor brtson ldan sgom pa po //
T02TD2727E:96b-1: sgrib pa rab spong shes rab dang //
T02TD2727E:96b-2: skal bzang nad med phun sum tshogs //
T02TD2727E:96b-4: bsgoms pas du ba na sems rtse gcig pas bzlas pa bya ste /
T02TD2727E:96b-7: 'di rnams ston ka'i rgyu skar dri ma med ba'i phreng ba lta bu'i kha dog dang 'od kyi snang ba can bas /
T02TD2727E:96b-8: 'od zer du ma 'phro bas bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD2727E:96b-9: dub par gyur na bsod nams yongs su bsdo zhing /
T02TD2727E:96b-10: langs pa ji ltar bde bar lha'i nga rgyal gyis gnas par bya'o //
T02TD2727E:96b-11: dpal ldan 'jig rten dbang phyug gi //
T02TD2727E:96b-12: yid 'ong sgrub thabs bgyis pa yis //
T02TD2727E:96b-13: bdag gis bsod nams gang thob des //
T02TD2727E:96b-15: dpal ldan 'jig rten mgon po kharsa p'a na'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba grub chen padma 'byung gnas zhabs kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2727E:96b-17: // / rgya gar shar phyogs kyi pandi ta chen po shr'i ba na ratna'i zhal snga nas dang /
T02TD2727E:96b-18: chos 'khor lo ts'a bas bsgyur ba las /
T02TD2727E:96b-19: slad kyis btsun pa rgya mtshos dag par bcos shing gtan la phab pa'o//
